game.name: Elsa Foot Injured
game.description:
Elsa is a very cute girl and loves playing outside when she gets bored at home. Today is not her day as she went outside with a happy face, but returned having some tears in her eyes. The problem is that her foot got injured when she was playing with her friends. Her family has taken her to the nearby clinic where they found no doctors available. Then they reminded of their family doctor. You are her family doctor, so join Elsa Foot Injured and get ready to give her the needful foot treatment. 
First diagnose the problem and give her a surgery, if needed, in this brand new doctor game for girls. You find all the medical tools on the screen. Follow the instructions as shown on the screen and help get her foot back! She trusts on your doctor skills completely, so feel free to make any experiments that could make her feel better. It is getting difficult for her to bear this pain right now. Treat her foot as fast as you can to bring her smile back on her face!
Use the ice cube on the bumps, and the employ the pliers to remove the splinter. Bandage the wound and then sprinkle some powder over there! Utilize the medicine dropper, heal the bruise, and then come to the injection to decrease her pain! Once it is done, you will Elsa with a happy face again in this one of the top games for girls.
